text: Molly Caitlyn Quinn (born October 8, 1993), also known as Molly C. Quinn, is an American actress. She is known for her roles in the television shows Castle and the English version of Winx Club. She also appeared in the movie We're the Millers (2013). Quinn was born in Texarkana, Texas.
